npm init 
npm i -D typescript
npx tsc --init
npx tsc   //Compaile typescript to javascript

Note:
1.Typescript give you compaile time error and js give you run time errro.
2. Typescript is only use in the development but when the code gets compaile for production all the type information will removed.

Lint
npm install --save-dev @typescript-eslint/parser @typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin eslint 
npx eslint .
npm install --save-dev eslint-config-prettier
npm run lint

Husky
npm install  husky@8.0.3  -D
npm pkg set scripts.prepare="husky install"
npm run prepare
npx husky add .husky/pre-commit "npm run lint"

Note
If module export defulat then we have import like import config from "dotenv";
but export const config then import { config } from "dotenv"; with {}

Logger
npm install winston
npm i -D @types/winston 

Error Handler 
npm install http-errors
npm i -D @types/http-errors

Jest
npm install --save-dev jest
npm install --save-dev ts-jest
npx ts-jest config:init
npm install --save-dev @types/jest
npm install -D  supertest
npm install -D  @types/supertest